                <li>Tax implications of federal grants (<a href="https://www.wisconsinctc.org">Wisconsin Center for Technology Commercialization</a>)</li>
                <li>SBIR/STTR grant examples (National Institutes of Health, <a href="https://nida.nih.gov/funding/small-business-innovation-research-sbir-technology-transfer-sttr-programs/resources/sample-applications">NIDA</a> and <a href="https://www.nia.nih.gov/research/sbir/nia-small-business-sample-applications">NIA</a>)</li>
